divs: Sighting Detailsafter watching the football game( pittsburgh vrs indianapolis, I went outside to smoke a cig and witnessed the prettiest shade of green that I ever saw shaped somewhat like a football come out of the west and headed towards boston. It moved in a staight line and then went out of sight. I felt kinda of happy as I enjoy seeing beautiful colors.I am retired and enjoy drawing and painting..,I cant describe the shade of green, never seen that shade before.
Summary: a bright green object whizzed by traveling west to east
